title: Yummy Chocolate Cake
ingredients: ['400g caster sugar', '250g plain flour', '4 tablespoons unsweetened cocoa powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1 teaspoon salt', '115g butter', '250ml water', '115ml buttermilk', '2 eggs, beaten', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract']
